<div id="Idea_3925"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3925-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3925">States Rights&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/8122-4049">bperrydore</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">2 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">The Tenth Amendment of the United States Constitution, which is part of the Bill of Rights, was ratified on December 15, 1791. The Tenth Amendment restates the Constitution's principle of Federalism by providing that powers not granted to the national government nor prohibited to the states are reserved to the states or the people.<br/><br/>"The powers not delegated to the United States by the Constitution, nor prohibited by it to the States, are reserved to the States respectively, or to the people."</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_3925" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_3925', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2247&topicID=3925')">Comments (9)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_3925"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2247">Between Federal, State, and Local Governments</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=states rights">states rights</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=federalism">federalism</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=abortion">abortion</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=gay marriage">gay marriage</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=legalazation of marijuana">legalazation of marijuana</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=bill of rights">bill of rights</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=tenth amendment">tenth amendment</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_3925"></div>
</div></td>
